<p><b>The Sherbrooke Hussars</b> is a <a href="/wiki/Primary_Reserve" title="Primary Reserve">Primary Reserve</a> <a href="/wiki/Armoured_warfare" title="Armoured warfare">armoured</a> <a href="/wiki/Regiment" title="Regiment">regiment</a> of the <a href="/wiki/Canadian_Forces" title="Canadian Forces" class="mw-redirect">Canadian Forces</a>.</p>
